flowchart TD
    PO[Purchase Order] --> Receive[Receive Pills\nShipment / Receive record]
    Receive --> QRPool[QR Card Pool\nRAW_BAG cards — idle]
    Receive --> InvBags[Inventory Bags\nweighed + batch-assigned]
    QRPool -->|reserved + assigned at receive| InvBags

    InvBags -->|bag with RELEASED batch| FloorStation[Floor Station Page\n/floor/token]
    FloorStation -->|scan bag QR| WorkflowEvents[workflow_events\nappend-only event log]

    WorkflowEvents -->|pg_notify → pg-boss projector| ReadModels[Read Models\nread_station_live\nread_bag_state\nread_daily_throughput]

    WorkflowEvents -->|BAG_FINALIZED| FinishedLots[Finished Lots\n+ Genealogy edges]

    FinishedLots --> ZohoQueue[Zoho Operations Queue\nzoho_operations]
    ZohoQueue -->|dry-run by default| ZohoGW[Zoho Integration Service\nLXC 9503]
    ZohoGW --> ZohoExternal[(Zoho Inventory / Books\nexternal downstream)]

    FloorBoard[Floor Board\nAdmin live view] -->|SSE stream| ReadModels

    subgraph Admin["Admin UI (office)"]
        FloorBoard
        QRAdmin[QR Card Admin]
        BatchAdmin[Batch Management]
        ProductAdmin[Products / Tablet Mappings]
        ReceivingAdmin[Receiving]
        ZohoOpsAdmin[Zoho Ops Queue UI]
    end

    QRAdmin -.->|manages| QRPool
    BatchAdmin -.->|manages| InvBags
    ProductAdmin -.->|configures| FloorStation
    ReceivingAdmin -.->|creates| Receive
    ZohoOpsAdmin -.->|monitors| ZohoQueue
